{"tid":1317531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(正式結束)祖雲達斯正式談妥迪列治，今晚將登機前往都靈，最遲明天早上體檢","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T11:11:34.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1a7dba26204d72cf785aae25c4fcf546013b76","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"7月14日訊 《米蘭體育報》消息，德利赫特將以7000萬歐加獎金的形式加盟尤文，這場漫長的轉會&ldquo;馬拉松&rdquo;已經正式結束。在經歷了長時間的談判後，阿賈克斯和尤文方面終於談妥，拉伊奧拉也表示滿意<br />\n據悉，今晚將登機前往都靈，最遲明天早上進行體檢，辦理各種手續。德利赫特的轉會費為7000萬歐元，另外加上複雜的獎金條款，他的合同將有1.5億歐的違約金條款。"},{"pid":"2020f4d88f29dc2a0ff03e4e9eddd92070de6d25","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:17:17.000Z","msg":"意大利媒體一致宣布德利格特即將跟尤文簽字。幾個月的連續劇結束！"},{"pid":"e7838edd4b777b73476bee92c4315c24ce8db819","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:18:33.000Z","msg":"屌我玩左幾個月,終於無得玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日要體驗官宣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de04b80f08c0661e21f51b57e4069f398876c86a","tid":1317531,"uid":43785,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e7838edd4b777b73476bee92c4315c24ce8db819","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:18:33.000Z","msg":"屌我玩左幾個月,終於無得玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日要體驗官宣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:36:00.000Z","msg":"點解 上機之前又出一篇文<br />\n<br />\n體檢之前洗唔洗都仲要出一篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n體檢之後又出一篇文<br />\n官方宣布之前又出一篇文"},{"pid":"e8567a1955f53b7e1c3cd5f9adb1ef4cad529689","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"de04b80f08c0661e21f51b57e4069f398876c86a","tid":1317531,"uid":43785,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e7838edd