ke":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"7月15日訊 據全市場網報導，迪列治即將加盟祖雲達斯。同時，全市場網還對迪列治轉會費以及合約細節進行了透露。迪列治的初始解約金將為1.25億歐，並將隨他的表現發生調整。<br />\n  報導稱，迪列治即將加盟祖雲達斯，他將成為全世界20歲的球員中年薪最高的球員。迪列治的稅後年薪將達到1200萬歐元，其中八成左右是固定年薪，剩下的是浮動獎金。報導稱，這部分獎金將與迪列治的表現掛鉤。<br />\n  報導指出，迪列治的解約金條款將為1.25億歐元，但這項解約金條款會根據迪列治的表現發生調整，如果迪列治表現出色，他的解約金條款也將變得更加昂貴。<br />\n  據悉，迪列治新賽季在祖雲達斯獲得的每一座冠軍，都將增加300萬歐元至400萬歐元的解約金。<br />\n  最後，報導稱，阿積士也會收到一筆非常可觀的轉會費。迪列治的轉會費將為7500萬歐元，其中包括獎金。"},{"pid":"ffa363150c05f7a6cb2fd8a45c04b86802ac47b9","tid":1317531,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82fad825de7a961578fd0b9b3550831e5366322f","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"7月15日訊 據全市場網報導，迪列治即將加盟祖雲達斯。同時，全市場網還對迪列治轉會費以及合約細節進行了透露。迪列治的初始解約金將為1.25億歐，並將隨他的表現發生調整。<br />\n  報導稱，迪列治即將加盟祖雲達斯，他將成為全世界20歲的球員中年薪最高的球員。迪列治的稅後年薪將達到1200萬歐元，其中八成左右是固定年薪，剩下的是浮動獎金。報導稱，這部分獎金將與迪列治的表現掛鉤。<br />\n  報導指出，迪列治的解約金條款將為1.25億歐元，但這項解約金條款會根據迪列治的表現發生調整，如果迪列治表現出色，他的解約金條款也將變得更加昂貴。<br />\n  據悉，迪列治新賽季在祖雲達斯獲得的每一座冠軍，都將增加300萬歐元至400萬歐元的解約金。<br />\n  最後，報導稱，阿積士也會收到一筆非常可觀的轉會費。迪列治的轉會費將為7500萬歐元，其中包括獎金。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e111e88c9bf6aef27c043c5104a898736db78c7","tid":1317531,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:53:20.000Z","msg":"最遲明天"},{"pid":"7e2780fcb79963c84eb097cfc3283510346301f2","tid":1317531,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:16:53.000Z","msg":"係咪體檢咗兩日？"},{"pid":"f6ac0fe30dcae6d8347f366635fc248cb4848caf","tid":1317531,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d15db3e527532397d550a8c0e13998365e299e","tid":1317531,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5cd784b9edfc022e9d256c93b8858b55e61f73","tid":1317531,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"幾時有波杉相"},{"pid":"a4cd639c41bc3fb51a00b5e43e9f288e85a0e16a","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"Matthijs De Ligt &egrave; atteso all&rsquo;aeroporto di Caselle di Torino intorno alle 22:30: l&rsquo;olandese &egrave; pronto a iniziare la sua avventura alla Juventus. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: calciomercato<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.calciomercato.com/news/juve-ecco-quando-arriva-de-ligt-88499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.calciomercato.com%2Fnews%2Fjuve-ecco-quando-arriva-de-ligt-88499&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=6eccd0b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.calciomercato.com/news/juve-ecco-quando-arriva-de-ligt-88499</a>"},{"pid":"22973b84cb70fd8de20f965e906f9f972bf9057c","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"迪列特意大利時間2230到都靈機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30388dbfeb0de37ae40aa81796361a00148ab74","tid":1317531,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22973b84cb70fd8de20f965e906f9f972bf9057c","tid":1317531,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"迪列特意大利時間2230到都靈機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"聽朝起身有波衫睇未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f13e3b0da1c1ed0d13c7862d6d894236d34896a","tid":1317531,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f30388dbfeb0de37ae40aa81796361a00148ab74","tid":1317531,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"